Class ArchiveController

java.lang.Object
  ca.ualberta.controllers.SCController
      ca.ualberta.controllers.BaseSelectionController
          ca.ualberta.controllers.ArchiveController

public class ArchiveController
extends BaseSelectionController

Implementation of the SCController class. Acts as the controller for ArchiveSelectionActivity. It subclasses BaseSelectionController so that it has the ability to retrieve photos, and populate the grid view. This controller is also responsible for actual process of archiving photos to the SD card.

Parameters:
photos - A shared list of PhotoEntry that contains all photos with a particular tag.
selected - A shared list of booleans that refer to the state of all the checkboxes associated with the photos.
tag - The tag of the photos to be displayed.
